          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " that he was more skeptical of single-payer. Then, when Democrats actually did win the presidency, the House and the Senate, Obama’s new presidential administration ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
