            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " about going out of its way to make sure the Affordable Care Act would prevent the creation of a single-payer health care system. Obama’s ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
